{"tid":1852480,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"專家王廣發治癒今出院 曾稱抗愛滋藥物對他有效","createTime":"2020-01-30T12:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T14:08:29.000Z","uid":104138,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"76382c664f77ba00f96dde175e25e5f179fd21db","tid":1852480,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續，國家衛健委專家組成員、北京大學第一醫院呼吸和危重症醫學科主任王廣發，早前赴武漢考察時也染病，確診新型冠狀病毒肺炎。內地傳媒報道，王廣發已治癒，今日在北京地壇醫院出院，精神不錯。<br />\n<br />\n他曾表示，一種對抗愛滋病病毒的藥物對他有效，令他病情好轉。但他也稱，對其他病患是否有效，需要後續觀察。<br />\n<br />\n王廣發是首位確診感染新型肺炎的專家組成員，他本月初曾隨國家衛健委專家組前往武漢，展開相關檢測核實工作，之後確診感染。<br />\n<br />\n曾稱疫情可控的王廣發，在隔離治療期間，他疏理自己可能感染的原因，稱自己曾到幾間醫院的發熱門診，但沒有配備防護眼鏡，而他回到北京後，出現結膜炎症狀，之後才出現發燒，他高度懷疑病毒先進入結膜，再到全身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2550000/2552303/0130020_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2550000%2F2552303%2F0130020_1024.jpg&h=b9abbcd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴左口罩都唔肯定係咪真人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />照計有解藥中共應該會認屎認屁"},{"pid":"4c388dd37d4c1d459cae7ddf9284e1a0076c485d","tid":1852480,"uid":161457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:41:21.000Z","msg":"係咪本身就有解藥 主動放出黎 武漢之前就有示威"},{"pid":"379b2e1faa6a9f89ba1b8e5dcbd325f223f62f17","tid":1852480,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"點會有解藥<br />\n話佢扮中招苦肉計好撚過啦"},{"pid":"d06261adde6750d4d017d358af856d65e28acd19","tid":1852480,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:47:50.000Z","msg":"本物個病可能低死亡率但超高傳染<br />\n呢種設定係利於病毒傳播<br />\n之所以死咁多人應該係太多人中招但無足夠人手處理<br />\n而王廣發應該有成十幾個人既團隊照住佢"},{"pid":"09b3fe5c8e0bc2642b9f8c95252405617484501d","tid":1852480,"uid":235754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"定係其實佢一早中咗愛滋 岩岩爆出黎啫呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a8c36308080da4b06b595a5a41179fae8ec0ce","tid":1852480,"uid":8745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:51:12.000Z","msg":"咁一定有人康復嘅<br />\n又唔係100%死亡率"},{"pid":"7127ed08e284277e5251dc812b96b29022f25bd1","tid":1852480,"uid":53411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"到底治癒病人<br />\n個肺有幾成功效<br />\n<br />\n定百分之百無問題？"},{"pid":"83398e7baee506b30c7a6268a8ec7f57a326dd36","tid":1852480,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"可能跟本無中招"},{"pid":"896a1b3c33482bd97fca7308d933fcc596d35b3c","tid":1852480,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"379b2e1faa6a9f89ba1b8e5dcbd325f223f62f17","tid":1852480,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"點會有解藥<br />\n話佢扮中招苦肉計好撚過啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:53:15.000Z","msg":"佢中招先笑死人喎可防可控"},{"pid":"ef9301354c15a9e37d2ed0b8f6fe13102c3a6d83","tid":1852480,"uid":43809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:53:18.000Z","msg":"愛滋扮肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb7fda4995096387b12666e00e03a7cf5309e67","tid":1852480,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:53:49.000Z","msg":"佢唔係肺炎係愛滋"},{"pid":"34c6e6f4af02413aa77cfa8098b5da691d7884a4","tid":1852480,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:55:19.000Z","msg":"死亡率10幾個%<br />\n你肯定係食藥醫好？<br />\n可能你呢個所謂專家係食屎所以好返"},{"pid":"0c958071a82023eecc458642ac0a3ff9b1347265","tid":1852480,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:58:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻暴